sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Host as HostUser
actor ParticipantUser as MeetingMember
participant Client as WebClient
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant MeetingCtrl as MeetingController
participant MeetingSvc as MeetingService
participant MeetingDb as MongoMeeting
participant VoiceNs as VoiceNamespace
participant SFU as MediasoupRoomManager

Host->>Client: Tao meeting
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/meetings
Gateway->>MeetingCtrl: createMeeting
MeetingCtrl->>MeetingSvc: validate context
MeetingSvc->>MeetingDb: insert meeting status scheduled
MeetingSvc-->>Client: 201

Host->>Client: Bat dau meeting
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/meetings/:id/start
Gateway->>MeetingCtrl: startMeeting
MeetingSvc->>MeetingDb: set active
MeetingSvc->>SFU: init room transport
MeetingSvc-->>Client: 200

ParticipantUser->>VoiceNs: join namespace voice
VoiceNs->>SFU: allocate peer transport
alt Meeting active and member valid
  SFU-->>ParticipantUser: join success + media params
else Meeting ended or forbidden
  SFU-->>ParticipantUser: reject join
end

Host->>Gateway: POST /api/meetings/:id/end
Gateway->>MeetingCtrl: endMeeting
MeetingSvc->>MeetingDb: set ended
MeetingSvc->>SFU: close room resources
